            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Full-depth competitive analysis quarterly, lightweight monitoring monthly. Set Google Alerts for competitor names, subscribe to their newsletters, and check their pricing pages once a month. Deep dives belong on a quarterly cadence.</p></div></div>
