            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Direct competitors sell the same product to the same audience — Coca-Cola vs Pepsi. Indirect competitors solve the same problem with a different approach — Coca-Cola vs bottled water. Most companies monitor 5-10 competitors: 3-5 direct and 2-5 indirect.</p></div></div>
